currentpacking true setpacking
/cg_md 141 dict def
cg_md begin
/L3? languagelevel 3 ge def
/bd{bind def}bind def
/ld{load def}bd
/xs{exch store}bd
/xd{exch def}bd
/cmmtx matrix def
mark
/sc/setcolor
/scs/setcolorspace
/dr/defineresource
/fr/findresource
/T/true
